title: For Sale:  VERY RARE Colt Camp Perry Pistol
postcontent: VERY RARE Colt Camp Perry Pistol. Stock # MSH240411SP. Serial # 13xx. One of HUNDREDS of Collectible, Antique, Military, Sporting , this is a magnificent find for the Serious Colt Collector, a very rare Colt Camp Perry Pistol. Made for the top-level target matches held at Camp Perry, Colt only produced 2500 of these pistols between the years 1920-1941.
